name: TTSLB_Archi_V1
description:
This is the effect _V1 version of the building By 囤囤鼠老白 (Mr.Ares)

The effect of viewing Angle is not bad, and the bird's eye view is also OK. If you want to express a clearer effect, please optimize your tag. The tag of a story can often produce good results.

Since it is the first version, many parts are not perfect, I hope users can help me find the problems together (the effect of people and cars in the picture is not very good at present, it is being improved).

It is not updated regularly, because there are still daily things, but I will keep on optimizing and improving.

I create Discord channel, channel will need to seek help questions: https://discord.gg/fVhyBXfE

Recommendations of use:

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Enable Quantization in ++K , ++SDE and DDIM samplers.

Hires. fix is needed for prompts where the character is far away in order to make decent images, it drastically improve the quality and detail of the buildings and landscape.

---------------------------------------------

Recommended parameters:

Sampler: Euler a: 40 to 60 steps.

Sampler: DPM++ SDE Karras: 30 to 60 steps.

Sampler: DPM++ 2M Karras: 20 to 60 steps.

CFG Scale: 7.5, 8.5 or 11 maybe is the best quality, you can try another.

Resolutions: 512x512, 1024x1024 for Architect and Landscape!

Hires. fix: R-ESRGAN 4x+ , with 30 steps at 0.5 denoising.

Negatives: ' (worst quality, low quality:1.5), (people:1.2),(car:1.2) '
